information: The company MM BEDACHUNGEN STUTTGART GMBH - DAS DICHTE DACH - ERBIS, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1931, which operates in the Indoor and greenhouse plants, floristry industry. It also operates in the Nurseries, Textile plants, Wood - sawn and treated, and Ceilings industries. It is based in Stuttgart, Germany.
